{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id79a935fb-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s3124"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3124"},"text":"§ 3124.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall prescribe such regulations as are necessary and appropriate to carry out his responsibilities under this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id79a935fc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/487/tVIII/s814"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–487, title VIII, § 814","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-12-02"},"text":"Dec. 2, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2429"},"text":"94 Stat. 2429","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/83/tIII/s316/b/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–83, title III, § 316(b)(8)","children":[],"tail":", (d), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-14"},"text":"Nov. 14, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/1594"},"text":"111 Stat. 1594","children":[],"tail":", 1595.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id79a935fd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id79a935fe-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id79a935ff-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1997—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/83/s316/b/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–83, § 316(b)(8)","children":[],"tail":", which directed amendment of section by inserting “, and the State at any time the State has complied with "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s3115/d"},"text":"section 3115(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":"” after “The Secretary” and inserting at end “During any time that the State has complied with "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s3115/d"},"text":"section 3115(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary shall not make or enforce regulations implementing section 3115(a), (b), or (c) of this title.”, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/83/s316/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–83, § 316(d)","children":[],"tail":". See Effective and Termination Dates of 1997 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id79a93600-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id79a93601-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective and Termination Dates of 1997 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Until laws are adopted in Alaska which provide for definition, preference, and participation specified in sections 3113 to 3115 of this title, amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/83"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–83","children":[],"tail":" was effective only for purpose of determining whether State’s laws provide for such definition, preference, and participation, and such amendment was repealed on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-12-01"},"text":"Dec. 1, 1998","children":[],"tail":",